wiki.content: A version of another Mingus composition, Haitian Fight Song. Charles Mingus - bass Booker Ervin - tenor sax Britt Woodman - trombone Don Butterfield - tuba Dick Hafer - tenor sax, clarinet Jerome Richardson - soprano, baritone saxes Eric Dolphy - alto sax Jaki Byard - piano Walter Perkins - drums The principal soloists are Ervin and Byard.
